            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <div class="role-head">
              <span class="role-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><ellipse cx="12" cy="5" rx="9" ry="3"/><path d="M3 5v14c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3V5"/><path d="M3 12c0 1.66 4 3 9 3s9-1.34 9-3"/></svg></span>
              <h4>Infra, netwerk &amp; cloud</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <div class="role-head">
              <span class="role-ic"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.9" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></span>
              <h4>Security &amp; compliance</h4>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="role-card">
            <div class="role-head">
